HEADWORD: Presumable
<hw>Pre*sum"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>pr⟦eacute⟧sumable</ets>.]</ety> <def>Such as may be presumed or
